    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;transmutation;\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;cleric/oracle 4, sorcerer/wizard 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;10 feet<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;one object of up to 5 lb./level<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;instantaneous<br>\n      <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless, object);&nbsp;\n      <strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell repairs 1d6 points of damage plus 1 point per level when cast on a construct creature (maximum 10d6+10).</p>\n<p><em>Greater <em>make whole</em></em> can fix destroyed magic items or technological items (items at 0 hit points or fewer), and restores the magic properties of the item if your caster level at least equal to that of the item. This spell otherwise functions as @Compendium[pf1.spells.x23pz2agjub1eh89]{Make Whole}.</p>\n</div>\n",
